<ab facs="#facs_518_r1l8">geleyte cʒu <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Vnd biten ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> fleiʒıklich </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_518_r1l9">daʒ Jr das von vns niht in vnwillen <expan>aufneme<ex>n</ex></expan> vvöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_518_r1l10"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden in <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſachen lıeb / dinſt / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_518_r1l11">wolgeuallen beweiſen möchten / des wern vvir wıllig </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_518_r1l12">vnd teten das allcʒeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ıa</expan> ıj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Exaltac<ex>i</ex>on<ex>is</ex></expan> </ab>
